menu "STM32"

menu "FcLink"

config STM32_FCLINK_TELEMETRY_RATE_HZ
    int "Telemetry rate (Hz)"
    range 1 255
    default 25
    help
      Requested STM32 telemetry publication rate for the FcLink protocol.

      ESP32 advertises this value back to STM32 during the FcLink handshake so
      both ends use the same telemetry-rate setting, but the user-facing
      ownership lives under the STM32 FcLink menu because it describes STM32
      telemetry behavior.

